The paper discusses transfer learning with convolutional networks, which is a common topic in machine learning and computer vision research. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses regularization schemes and inductive bias, which are topics that fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper uses natural language processing as an example, which suggests that it could also be relevant to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
